      <title>穆巴达拉资本将重启巴西竞争对手交易所计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/mubadala-capital-to-revive-plans-for-rival-exchange-in-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，阿布扎比主权财富基金的全资子公司穆巴达拉资本 (Mubadala Capital) 计划在巴西设立一家证券交易所，通过其去年收购的一家公司与 B3 交易所竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/mubadala-capital-to-revive-plans-for-rival-exchange-in-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 14:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
